    "documentHtml": "<div class=\"bjelke\">Den fulde tekst</div><p class=\"Titel2\">Bekendtgørelse om tilbageførsel af aktivitetsbestemt medfinansiering af sundhedsvæsenet ud over regionalt indtægtsloft til kommunerne for 2016</p>\r\n<p class=\"Indledning2\">I medfør af § 13, stk. 2, og § 14 a i lov om regionernes finansiering, jf. lovbekendtgørelse nr. 797 af 27. juni 2011, som ændret ved lov nr. 1735 af 27. december 2016, fastsættes:</p>\r\n<p class=\"ParagrafGruppeOverskrift\">\r\n   <span>Afrunding</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"Paragraf\" id=\"id1d6a949e-4445-46e5-ac3a-b51a49fbd322\">\r\n   <span id=\"P1\">\r\n   </span>\r\n   <span class=\"ParagrafNr\" id=\"Par1\">§ 1.</span> Tilbagebetalingen opgøres i hele 1.000 kr.</p>\r\n<p class=\"ParagrafGruppeOverskrift\">\r\n   <span>Opgørelse af tilbageførsel af aktivitetsbestemt medfinansiering af sundhedsvæsenet ud over regionalt indtægtsloft</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"Paragraf\" id=\"id1dfb8e64-c9c8-4728-a92e-f7bada5a73f6\">\r\n   <span id=\"P2\">\r\n   </span>\r\n   <span class=\"ParagrafNr\" id=\"Par2\">§ 2.</span> Det forudsatte niveau for de kommunale udgifter til kommunal aktivitetsbestemt medfinansiering, jf. BEK nr. 1014 af 28. juni 2016 19.743.500 tusinde kr. og opgjort på regionsniveau:</p>\r\n<p class=\"TekstGenerel\">\r\n   <div style=\"width:100%\">\r\n      <table class=\"Containertable\" style=\"border-style: none; border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px; margin: 0.2cm 0cm 0cm 0cm; \">\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"border-style: none; padding: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">\r\n               <table valign=\"top\" class=\"Maintable\" width=\"310\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse;\">\r\n                  <colgroup>\r\n                     <col width=\"113px\">\r\n                     </col>\r\n                     <col width=\"119px\">\r\n                     </col>\r\n                  </colgroup>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;padding-left:0cm;padding-top:0cm;padding-right:0cm;padding-bottom:0cm;\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">1) Region Nordjylland:</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;padding-left:0cm;padding-top:0cm;padding-right:0cm;padding-bottom:0cm;text-align: right\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">1.823.577 tusinde kr.</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;padding-left:0cm;padding-top:0cm;padding-right:0cm;padding-bottom:0cm;\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">2) Region Midtjylland:</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;padding-left:0cm;padding-top:0cm;padding-right:0cm;padding-bottom:0cm;text-align: right\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">4.177.984 tusinde kr.</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;padding-left:0cm;padding-top:0cm;padding-right:0cm;padding-bottom:0cm;\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">3) Region Syddanmark:</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;padding-left:0cm;padding-top:0cm;padding-right:0cm;padding-bottom:0cm;text-align: right\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">4.287.352 tusinde kr.</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;padding-left:0cm;padding-top:0cm;padding-right:0cm;padding-bottom:0cm;\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">4) Region Hovedstaden:</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;padding-left:0cm;padding-top:0cm;padding-right:0cm;padding-bottom:0cm;text-align: right\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">6.430.478 tusinde kr.</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;padding-left:0cm;padding-top:0cm;padding-right:0cm;padding-bottom:0cm;\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">5) Region Sjælland:</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;padding-left:0cm;padding-top:0cm;padding-right:0cm;padding-bottom:0cm;text-align: right\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">3.024.109 tusinde kr.</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n               </table>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n      </table>\r\n   </div>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"TekstGenerel\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"Stk2\">\r\n   <span class=\"StkNr\" id=\"idb33865ca-8d0e-4fa9-85b3-6c27974eb208\">Stk. 2.</span> De opgjorte afregninger til den kommunale aktivitetsbestemte medfinansiering for 2016 er af Sundhedsdatastyrelsen opgjort til at udgøre i alt 19.841.195 tusinde kr. og opgjort på regionsniveau:</p>\r\n<p class=\"TekstGenerel\">\r\n   <div style=\"width:100%\">\r\n      <table class=\"Containertable\" style=\"border-style: none; border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px; margin: 0.2cm 0cm 0cm 0cm; \">\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"border-style: none; padding: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">\r\n               <table valign=\"top\" class=\"Maintable\" width=\"310\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse;\">\r\n                  <colgroup>\r\n                     <col width=\"113px\">\r\n                     </col>\r\n                     <col width=\"119px\">\r\n                     </col>\r\n                  </colgroup>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;padding-left:0cm;padding-top:0cm;padding-right:0cm;padding-bottom:0cm;\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">1) Region Nordjylland:</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;padding-left:0cm;padding-top:0cm;padding-right:0cm;padding-bottom:0cm;text-align: right\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">1.846.837 tusinde kr.</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;padding-left:0cm;padding-top:0cm;padding-right:0cm;padding-bottom:0cm;\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">2) Region Midtjylland:</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;padding-left:0cm;padding-top:0cm;padding-right:0cm;padding-bottom:0cm;text-align: right\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">4.204.173 tusinde kr.</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;padding-left:0cm;padding-top:0cm;padding-right:0cm;padding-bottom:0cm;\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">3) Region Syddanmark:</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;padding-left:0cm;padding-top:0cm;padding-right:0cm;padding-bottom:0cm;text-align: right\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">4.282.693 tusinde kr.</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;padding-left:0cm;padding-top:0cm;padding-right:0cm;padding-bottom:0cm;\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">4) Region Hovedstaden:</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;padding-left:0cm;padding-top:0cm;padding-right:0cm;padding-bottom:0cm;text-align: right\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">6.430.861 tusinde kr.</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;padding-left:0cm;padding-top:0cm;padding-right:0cm;padding-bottom:0cm;\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">5) Region Sjælland:</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;padding-left:0cm;padding-top:0cm;padding-right:0cm;padding-bottom:0cm;text-align: right\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">3.076.631 tusinde kr.</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n               </table>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n      </table>\r\n   </div>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"TekstGenerel\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"Stk2\">\r\n   <span class=\"StkNr\" id=\"id4b45bb37-6642-47c9-a8ae-0b2efe4adec4\">Stk. 3.</span> Den positive forskel mellem stk. 1 og stk. 2. er midlertidig opsamlet på finanslovkonto 16.51.91 og udgør i alt 102.354 tusinde kr. og opgjort på regionsniveau:</p>\r\n<p class=\"TekstGenerel\">\r\n   <div style=\"width:100%\">\r\n      <table class=\"Containertable\" style=\"border-style: none; border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px; margin: 0.2cm 0cm 0cm 0cm; \">\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"border-style: none; padding: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">\r\n               <table valign=\"top\" class=\"Maintable\" width=\"310\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse;\">\r\n                  <colgroup>\r\n                     <col width=\"113px\">\r\n                     </col>\r\n                     <col width=\"119px\">\r\n                     </col>\r\n                  </colgroup>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;padding-left:0cm;padding-top:0cm;padding-right:0cm;padding-bottom:0cm;\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">1) Region Nordjylland:</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;padding-left:0cm;padding-top:0cm;padding-right:0cm;padding-bottom:0cm;text-align: right\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">23.260 tusinde kr.</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;padding-left:0cm;padding-top:0cm;padding-right:0cm;padding-bottom:0cm;\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">2) Region Midtjylland:</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;padding-left:0cm;padding-top:0cm;padding-right:0cm;padding-bottom:0cm;text-align: right\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">26.189 tusinde kr.</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;padding-left:0cm;padding-top:0cm;padding-right:0cm;padding-bottom:0cm;\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">3) Region Syddanmark:</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;padding-left:0cm;padding-top:0cm;padding-right:0cm;padding-bottom:0cm;text-align: right\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">- tusinde kr.</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;padding-left:0cm;padding-top:0cm;padding-right:0cm;padding-bottom:0cm;\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">4) Region Hovedstaden:</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;padding-left:0cm;padding-top:0cm;padding-right:0cm;padding-bottom:0cm;text-align: right\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">383 tusinde kr.</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;padding-left:0cm;padding-top:0cm;padding-right:0cm;padding-bottom:0cm;\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">5) Region Sjælland:</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;padding-left:0cm;padding-top:0cm;padding-right:0cm;padding-bottom:0cm;text-align: right\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">52.522 tusinde kr.</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n               </table>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n      </table>\r\n   </div>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"TekstGenerel\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"Stk2\">\r\n   <span class=\"StkNr\" id=\"ide162d94a-5b12-4cd8-9ca3-999630c9329d\">Stk. 4.</span> Den i stk. 3 opgjorte opsamling fordeles mellem de enkelte kommuner i den pågældende region i forhold til den enkelte kommunes andel af regionens befolkningstal, jf. Tabel 3. ’Data til opgørelse af beskatningsgrundlag 2016’, søjle (12), fra publikationen ’Kommunal udligning og generelle tilskud 2016’, juli 2015, Social og indenrigsministeriet.</p>\r\n<p class=\"ParagrafGruppeOverskrift\">\r\n   <span>Endelig opgørelse om tilbagebetaling af kommunal medfinansiering samt anvisning</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"Paragraf\" id=\"idf75a6aa8-c269-4877-bfd0-df318c1b1cf4\">\r\n   <span id=\"P3\">\r\n   </span>\r\n   <span class=\"ParagrafNr\" id=\"Par3\">§ 3.</span> Sundhedsdatastyrelsen giver via informationssystemet eSundhed meddelelse til kommunalbestyrelserne om den endelige opgørelse efter § 2, stk. 4. senest den 20. juli, eller førstkommende hverdag herefter.</p>\r\n<p class=\"Stk2\">\r\n   <span class=\"StkNr\" id=\"id0560daf6-cf2f-455c-9897-857e4c1d1cb9\">Stk. 2.</span> Sundhedsdatastyrelsen anviser tilbagebetalingen af den kommunale medfinansiering efter § 2, stk. 4.</p>\r\n<p class=\"Stk2\">\r\n   <span class=\"StkNr\" id=\"idae3bf7b6-cd78-48cc-a772-552f24426c0f\">Stk. 3.</span> Betalingerne efter stk. 2 afregnes via, kommunens og statens konti i Offentligt BetalingsSystem (OBS) i henhold til gældende regler om dette system.</p>\r\n<p class=\"Paragraf\" id=\"id19844a94-6831-449d-89cc-b82c2fe9d62b\">\r\n   <span id=\"P4\">\r\n   </span>\r\n   <span class=\"ParagrafNr\" id=\"Par4\">§ 4.</span> Bekendtgørelsen træder i kraft den 1. juli 2017.</p><div class=\"Givet\" id=\"Givet\"><p class=\"Givet\" align=\"center\">Sundheds- og Ældreministeriet, den 27. juni 2017</p><p class=\"Sign1\" align=\"center\">Ellen Trane Nørby</p><p class=\"Sign2\" align=\"right\">/ Charlotte Hougaard Clifford</p></div>",
